      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-08/ubs-moriya-on-japan-markets-strategy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银证券日本股票策略师 Nozomi Moriya 讨论了她对日本股市的展望和投资策略。她与 Shery Ahn 和 Haidi Stroud-Watts 就“彭博：亚洲交易”进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
